Notes:
*First and last names are made by trying to split viewer names in two with a '_' or '.'
*Names will be applied dynamically and are not saved with save game or city data. They will be reset across play sessions.
*No personal information is saved, and names will be applied to citizens randomly.
Displayed Text:
* Jmena a prijmeni jsou vytvorena tak, ze se pokusite rozdelit jmena prohlizecu na dve casti pomoci znaku '_' nebo '.'
* Jmena se pouziji dynamicky a neukladaji se s ulozenymi daty hry nebo mesta. Budou resetovana napric hernimi relacemi.
*Neukladaji se zadne osobni udaje a jmena budou na obcany aplikovana nahodne.
